keymap settings.

1. sudo dumpkeys | sudo tee -a defkeymap.map
2. sudo cp defkeymap.map mykeymap.map
3. add following lines to the end of mykeymap.map

# Zenkaku Hankaku -> Esc
keycode 41 = Escape
# Tab       -> Shift
keycode 15 = Shift
# Caps Lock -> Ctrl
keycode 58 = Control
# Shift_L   -> Alt
keycode 42 = Alt
# Alt       -> Caps Lock
keycode 56 = Caps_Lock
# Muhenkan  -> Tab
keycode 94 = Tab

4. sudo loadkeys mykeymap.map
